<tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><img border="0" src="../triangle.JPG"><font size="3" face="Tahoma" color="#004242"><b>LAMBENT BOOTS</b></font></p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Class:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Bard</b></font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Minimum Level:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">30</font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Estimated Quest Length:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">3 hours</font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Quest NPC:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Walthin Fireweaver</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Starting Zone:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Temple of Solusek Ro&Comment=1">Temple of Solusek Ro</a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Secondary Zones:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Solusek A&Comment=1">Solusek A</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Karana, West&Comment=1">Karana, West</a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Items Needed:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Lambent Sapphire</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Middle Portion of the Rune of the One Eye</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Firewalker Boots</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Lambent Stone</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Description:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>1.</b> This quest begins in the Temple of Solusek Ro.  <b>Walthin Fireweaver</b>, a Half Elf Bard at loc +430 -50, asks for three items in order to make you the Lambent Boots: a Lambent Sapphire, the middle portion of the Rune of the One Eye, and the Firewalker Boots.
<br><br>
<b>2.</b> Since you are nearby, you should first obtain the <b>Firewalker Boots</b>.  Head to Solusek A and look for the <b>Solusek Mage</b>.  He spawns near the Solusek Goblin King room, at loc -810 -460.  He may also spawn at loc -1000 -640.  The Solusek Mage is a level 28 to 30 Goblin Wizard with roughly 1000 HPs.  Kill him and loot the Firewalker Boots.
<br><br>
<b>3.</b> You must now obtain the <b>Middle Portion of the Rune of the One Eye</b>.  As the name suggests, it is dropped by a Cyclops named <b>Froon</b>.  You can find him in West Karana at loc -1270 -8720.  Froon is level 30 with roughly 1700 HPs.  Kill him and loot the Rune.
<br><br>
<b>4.</b> The last item you need to obtain, the <b>Lambent Sapphire</b>, is a little trickier.  To get one, you need 2 Sapphires and 1 Lambent Stone.  Sapphires can be purchased from most gem vendors, but Lambent Stones must be looted from random high level mobs such as Hill Giants and Sand Giants.  So go ahead and kill these creatures until you get yourself a Lambent Stone.
<br><br>
<b>5.</b> Now purchase 2 Sapphires and return to the Temple of Solusek Ro.  Look for <b>Gardern</b> on top of the balcony, at loc +430 -60.  Give him the 2 Sapphires and the Lambent Stone and he will give you the Lambent Sapphire.  Click <a href="http://www.eqinsider.com/quests/questdetails.asp?Guide=46">here</a> for more information regarding the Lambent Gem Mini Quests.
<br><br>
<b>6.</b> You now have all 3 items needed to complete this quest.  Return to <b>Walthin</b> and give them to him.  He will then reward you with the Lambent Boots.</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Author:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Wraith (Bristlebane)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Quest Reward:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Lambent Boots</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma"></font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>AC+11, CHA+1, SV Fire+2, SV Disease+2, SV Cold+2, SV Magic+2, SV Poison+2</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rating:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>8</b> (average of <b>2</b> votes)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rate this quest:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><FORM ACTION = "ratequest.asp" METHOD = post><SELECT NAME="Voting"><OPTION VALUE="0">Rate